  "page": "Cider Hall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Cider Hall</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nHall</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Feudalism\" title=\"Feudalism\">feudal lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Religion</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/400px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/800px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 38.9%; left: 63.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -6px; top: -6px; width: 12px; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Cider Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Cider Hall\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/18px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/24px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Cider Hall</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">The Reach</a> and the location of Cider Hall\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cider Hall</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. It is located near the confluence of the <a href=\"/index.php/Cockleswhent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cockleswhent\">Cockleswhent</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The castle is named after the <a href=\"/index.php/Cider\" title=\"Cider\">alcoholic beverage</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cider_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Florence_Fossoway\" title=\"Florence Fossoway\">Florence Fossoway</a>, the wife of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Tyrell\" title=\"Martyn Tyrell\">Martyn Tyrell</a>, became skilled at numbers by counting apples as a child.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Franklyn_Flowers\" title=\"Franklyn Flowers\">Franklyn Flowers</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a>, his mother was a washerwoman at Cider Hall who was raped by one of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">Fossoway's</a> sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cider_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne - Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, The Lost Lord.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Flowers says <i>«one of milord's sons»</i>, which is inaccurate, because the Fossoways of Cider Hall have been a knightly house at least since <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Reach\" title=\"Template:Region Reach\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region Reach (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_Rea